  "pageTitle": "現代資源回收設施的兩套系統",
  "bodyHtml": "<main class=\"product-page\">\n      <section class=\"section page-hero\" aria-labelledby=\"products-title\">\n        <p class=\"eyebrow\">產品線</p>\n        <h1 id=\"products-title\">現代資源回收設施的兩套系統</h1>\n        <p class=\"hero-copy\">比較AI可回收塑膠的光學分揀系統，以及建築、裝飾、拆除及大型廢棄物專案的整合式C&D廢棄物回收管線。</p>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section product-family-intro\" id=\"product-comparison\" aria-labelledby=\"product-families-title\">\n        <p class=\"eyebrow\">獨立解族</p>\n        <h2 id=\"product-families-title\">兩條不同的專案路徑，而不是同一目錄的兩個變體</h2>\n        <p>其中一款產品家族專為高價值塑膠識別與光學分揀而打造。另一座則用於C&D及大型廢棄物專案中的重型破碎、篩選及資源利用。</p>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"product-family-band product-family-ai\" aria-labelledby=\"ai-family-title\">\n        <div class=\"product-family-inner\">\n          <picture class=\"product-family-media\">\n            <img src=\"/assets/images/super-sorting.jpg\" alt=\"WEI LAN 超光學分揀系統配置與模組化分揀設備\">\n          </picture>\n          <div class=\"product-family-content\">\n            <p class=\"eyebrow\">超光學分揀系統</p>\n            <h2 id=\"ai-family-title\">AI 可回收塑膠光學分揀中心</h2>\n            <p>模組化分選模組可依材質與顏色識別並區分PET瓶、HDPE瓶、PP及混合塑膠。</p>\n            <div class=\"product-family-chips\" aria-label=\"典型材料\">\n              <span>PET瓶</span>\n              <span>HDPE瓶</span>\n              <span>PP 塑膠</span>\n              <span>混合可回收物</span>\n            </div>\n            <dl class=\"product-family-metrics\" aria-label=\"AI 光學分鏡亮點\">\n              <div>\n                <dt>0.6-2 t/h</dt>\n                <dd>吞吐量範圍</dd>\n              </div>\n              <div>\n                <dt>5-10</dt>\n                <dd>物料類別</dd>\n              </div>\n              <div>\n                <dt>滑架模組</dt>\n                <dd>更快的安裝</dd>\n              </div>\n            </dl>\n            <p class=\"product-action-strip\"><a class=\"text-link\" href=\"/products/ai-optical-sorting\" aria-label=\"查看AI光學分揀系統 詳情\">查看詳情</a></p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"product-family-band product-family-industrial\" aria-labelledby=\"industrial-family-title\">\n        <div class=\"product-family-inner\">\n          <div class=\"product-family-content\">\n            <p class=\"eyebrow\">建設與大型廢棄物管線</p>\n            <h2 id=\"industrial-family-title\">整合式C&D廢棄物處理與資源利用線</h2>\n            <p>Lion One整合破碎與篩選站結合了給料、破碎、篩分、磁性分離、氣流分離及打包設備。</p>\n            <div class=\"product-engineering-brief\">\n              <ol class=\"product-process-chain\" aria-label=\"核心C&D 廢棄物處理流程\">\n                <li>給料</li>\n                <li>破碎</li>\n                <li>篩分</li>\n                <li>磁分離</li>\n                <li>氣流分離</li>\n                <li>打包</li>\n              </ol>\n              <dl class=\"product-line-specs\" aria-label=\"C&D 廢棄物線重點\">\n                <div>\n                  <dt>容量範圍</dt>\n                  <dd>20-70 t/h</dd>\n                </div>\n                <div>\n                  <dt>單機使用範圍</dt>\n                  <dd>35 m<sup>2</sup></dd>\n                </div>\n                <div>\n                  <dt>可調整壓碎尺寸</dt>\n                  <dd>液壓驅動</dd>\n                </div>\n              </dl>\n            </div>\n            <p class=\"product-action-strip\">\n              <a class=\"text-link\" href=\"/products/construction-waste-recycling-line\" aria-label=\"查看建築廢棄管線規格\">查看詳情</a>\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <picture class=\"product-family-media\">\n            <img src=\"/assets/images/lion-mark1.jpg\" alt=\"WEI LAN建築與裝飾廢棄物的綜合破碎與篩選站\">\n          </picture>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"contact-section\" aria-labelledby=\"products-inquiry-title\">\n        <div>\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">計畫探究</p>\n          <h2 id=\"products-inquiry-title\">寄出你的材料和容量需求</h2>\n          <p>請分享你正在評估的廢棄物流、目標吞吐量、場址限制及專案階段。WEI LAN可以推薦合適的產品線，並準備更專注的提案討論。</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"about-contact-panel compact-contact-panel\">\n          <a class=\"primary-button\" href=\"/contact\">請求產品提案</a>\n          <a class=\"secondary-button\" href=\"/solutions\">審查解決方案路徑</a>\n          <p>銷售熱線：+86 137 8001 2268 / +86 180 6737 7770</p>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"section\" id=\"specs\" aria-labelledby=\"specs-title\" hidden>\n        <div class=\"section-heading\">\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">規格</p>\n          <h2 id=\"specs-title\">核心乘積參數</h2>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"spec-group spec-group-ai\" aria-labelledby=\"spec-group-ai\">\n          <header class=\"spec-group-head\">\n            <span class=\"spec-group-tag\">超光學分揀</span>\n            <h3 id=\"spec-group-ai\">GL01V系列</h3>\n          </header>\n          <div class=\"spec-card-grid\">\n            <article class=\"spec-card spec-card-ai is-tier-1\">\n              <header class=\"spec-card-head\">\n                <span class=\"spec-card-rank\">SYS-01</span>\n                <div class=\"spec-card-id\">\n                  <p class=\"spec-card-model\">GL01V1-5</p>\n                  <p class=\"spec-card-tier\">迷你</p>\n                </div>\n                <span class=\"spec-card-status\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                  <i></i><i></i>\n                </span>\n              </header>\n              <dl class=\"spec-metrics\">\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:35%\">\n                  <dt>容量</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">0.6&ndash;0.8<small>T/H</small></span></dd>\n                  <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:55%\">\n                  <dt>動力</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">30<small>千瓦</small></span></dd>\n                  <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:38%\">\n                  <dt>佔地</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">24<small>m<sup>2</sup></small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">安裝面積 ·8 × 3 m 版面 ·3 m 淨空高度</span></dd>\n                  <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:50%\">\n                  <dt>分選範圍</dt>\n                  <dd class=\"spec-scope\"><span class=\"spec-value\">5<small>物料類型</small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix spec-scope-summary\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-label=\"完整分選範圍：透明PET·彩色PET ·HDPE ·PP ·混合塑膠\" data-scope-detail=\"clear PET · color PET · HDPE · PP · mixed plastics\">PET ·HDPE ·PP ·混合</span></dd>\n                  <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n                </div>\n              </dl>\n            </article>\n\n            <article class=\"spec-card spec-card-ai is-tier-2\">\n              <header class=\"spec-card-head\">\n                <span class=\"spec-card-rank\">SYS-02</span>\n                <div class=\"spec-card-id\">\n                  <p class=\"spec-card-model\">GL01V2-9</p>\n                  <p class=\"spec-card-tier\">標準</p>\n                </div>\n                <span class=\"spec-card-status\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                  <i></i><i></i>\n                </span>\n              </header>\n              <dl class=\"spec-metrics\">\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:58%\">\n                  <dt>容量</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">0.8&ndash;1.2<small>T/H</small></span></dd>\n                  <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:78%\">\n                  <dt>動力</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">45<small>千瓦</small></span></dd>\n                  <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:62%\">\n                  <dt>佔地</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">36<small>m<sup>2</sup></small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">安裝面積 ·12 × 3 m 版面 ·6 m 淨空高度</span></dd>\n                  <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:90%\">\n                  <dt>分選範圍</dt>\n                  <dd class=\"spec-scope\"><span class=\"spec-value\">9<small>物料類型</small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix spec-scope-summary\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-label=\"完整分選範圍：透明PET·綠PET ·藍色PET ·混色PET·白HDPE·有色HDPE·PP ·混合塑膠·拒絕\" data-scope-detail=\"clear PET · green PET · blue PET · mixed-color PET · white HDPE · colored HDPE · PP · mixed plastics · reject\">PET 顏色 ·HDPE ·PP ·混合·拒絕</span></dd>\n                  <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n                </div>\n              </dl>\n            </article>\n\n            <article class=\"spec-card spec-card-ai is-tier-3\">\n              <header class=\"spec-card-head\">\n                <span class=\"spec-card-rank\">SYS-03</span>\n                <div class=\"spec-card-id\">\n                  <p class=\"spec-card-model\">GL01V3-10</p>\n                  <p class=\"spec-card-tier\">Plus</p>\n                </div>\n                <span class=\"spec-card-status\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                  <i></i><i></i>\n                </span>\n              </header>\n              <dl class=\"spec-metrics\">\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:95%\">\n                  <dt>容量</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">1.5&ndash;2<small>T/H</small></span></dd>\n                  <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:92%\">\n                  <dt>動力</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">53<small>千瓦</small></span></dd>\n                  <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:92%\">\n                  <dt>佔地</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">51<small>m<sup>2</sup></small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">安裝面積 ·17 × 3 m 版面 ·6 m 淨空高度</span></dd>\n                  <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:100%\">\n                  <dt>分選範圍</dt>\n                  <dd class=\"spec-scope\"><span class=\"spec-value\">10<small>物料類型</small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix spec-scope-summary\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-label=\"完整分選範圍：透明PET·綠PET ·藍色PET ·混色PET·白HDPE·有色HDPE·PP ·PE ·混合塑膠·拒絕\" data-scope-detail=\"clear PET · green PET · blue PET · mixed-color PET · white HDPE · colored HDPE · PP · PE · mixed plastics · reject\">PET 顏色 ·HDPE ·PP ·PE ·混合·拒絕</span></dd>\n                  <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div>\n                </div>\n              </dl>\n            </article>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"spec-group spec-group-industrial\" aria-labelledby=\"spec-group-cdw\">\n          <header class=\"spec-group-head\">\n            <span class=\"spec-group-tag\">C&D 廢棄物線</span>\n            <h3 id=\"spec-group-cdw\">Lion One綜合車站</h3>\n          </header>\n          <div class=\"spec-card-grid spec-card-grid-wide\">\n            <article class=\"spec-card spec-card-industrial\">\n              <header class=\"spec-card-head\">\n                <span class=\"spec-card-rank\">L1</span>\n                <div class=\"spec-card-id\">\n                  <p class=\"spec-card-model\">Lion One</p>\n                  <p class=\"spec-card-tier\">綜合破碎與篩選站</p>\n                </div>\n                <dl class=\"spec-card-plate\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                  <div><dt>製造集團</dt><dd>WEI&nbsp;LAN</dd></div>\n                  <div><dt>類型</dt><dd>行動&nbsp;電台</dd></div>\n                  <div><dt>等級</dt><dd>重型&nbsp;</dd></div>\n                </dl>\n              </header>\n              <dl class=\"spec-metrics spec-metrics-wide\">\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\">\n                  <dt>容量</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">20&ndash;70</span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">T/H</span></dd>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\">\n                  <dt>進給尺寸</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">200</span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">mm</span></dd>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\">\n                  <dt>佔地</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">35</span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">m<sup>2</sup> · 11.7 × 3 × 3.1 m</span></dd>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"spec-metric\">\n                  <dt>驅動</dt>\n                  <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">100<small>%</small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">全液壓</span></dd>\n                </div>\n              </dl>\n              <footer class=\"spec-card-foot\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n                <span class=\"spec-card-foot-mark\">WEI LAN</span>\n                <span class=\"spec-card-foot-sep\"></span>\n                <span>寧波，中國</span>\n                <span class=\"spec-card-foot-sep\"></span>\n                <span>整合行動台</span>\n              </footer>\n            </article>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n    </main>"
}
